### 5. Utility that extracts tag text (and throws on absence)
**File:** `core/lib/src/utils/xml_utils.dart`, lines 3–15

```dart
String tagContents(xml.XmlElement node, String tagName) {
  final contents = tagContentsOrNull(node, tagName);
  if (contents == null) {
    throw ArgumentError('Contents for $tagName were unexpectedly null.'); // line 7
